I get a lot of questions but couldn't answer them all on IG live, I'll try to get them covered in my YouTube videos!

node.text:
✨Art girl makes books✨

When I’m not making comics, I illustrate books! That’s how I make a living. “Everyday, Chemistry” is a cozy book about a mum and daughter finding chemistry reactions in daily activities. Written by @julia_sooy and published by #feiwelandfriends . I had a lot of fun drawing this book.

I also updated my website with book info and purchase links! If you’d like to buy a copy or browse my other books, please head to the link on my profile💕

P.S. Had the idea of having Big Brown introduce the book, a great way to support him otherwise he’d be a pile of bear skin.. 😂

node.text:
🥦Giveaway time!🥦

IT Guy is not into video games, but we do enjoy playing card games! “Abandon All Artichokes” is a card game I illustrated earlier this year, featuring a variety of funny vegetables. I had a great time working with Gamewright making this game, and we are giving away 3 of them😊

How to Enter: ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

1️. LIKE this photo

2️. FOLLOW @bonniepangart and @gamewright

3️. TAG a veggie-loving friend in the comments.

Giveaway will be open until 6/26 at midnight EDT.  To enter you must be 18+ years old and one entry per person. Open worldwide. Three random winners will be chosen from the Facebook and Instagram entries to receive one copy of Abandon All Artichokes. This giveaway is in no way associated with Instagram. 

#cardgame #abandonallartichokes #itguyartgirl #bonniepangart
